went to \"logout\", which is not the most user-intuitive).\n\nAs a result of this report, we rethought how we handled password changes, and we decided to invalidate all sessions on a password change/reset to protect from this possible problem.","can_view?":true,"can_create?":false,"attachments":[],"user":{"id":3132,"username":"reed","name":"Reed Loden","bio":"The guy who does the thing. Security @ HackerOne.","cleared":false,"website":"https://reedloden.com","location":"San Francisco, CA","created_at":"2014-02-27T22:34:29.323Z","url":"https://hackerone.com/reed","anc_triager":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false,"user_type":"company","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/132/66d7eadcea16b878bb67bfd697b9542250a801a7_original.jpg/43e4513b9104ea0d68c9c096cea374ba8440dde3e027af5465c8771e8839a67c","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/132/66d7eadcea16b878bb67bfd697b9542250a801a7_original.jpg/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c","xtralarge":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/132/66d7eadcea16b878bb67bfd697b9542250a801a7_original.jpg/c11036e2d3f8b05af4b5da5984ccdec6f786b763c8abceb4e68042e10dcdae85"}}},{"id":1766,"category":"researcher","content":"Existing user sessions wasn't getting destroyed when a HackerOne user changed his password from account panel or through password reset token!\nHackerOne was aware of this issue, but didn't consider it as an immediate fix as another fix (all active sessions invalidates when user logout from account) was in place. \nAs a result of this report, HackerOne team decided to invalidate all sessions on a password change/reset to protect from this possible problem.\n\nThanks to HackerOne team for fixing this issue and the bounty! ","can_view?":true,"can_create?":false,"attachments":[],"user":{"id":3726,"username":"faisalahmed","name":"Faisal Ahmed","bio":"Infosec enthusiast, Bug bounty participant","cleared":true,"website":"https://faisalahmed.me","location":"Bradford, United Kingdom","created_at":"2014-03-19T12:56:16.024Z","url":"https://hackerone.com/faisalahmed","anc_triager":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false,"hacker_resume_enabled":true,"user_type":"hacker","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/726/e66916f9112a11c1e97ec5ea0ad886121d14f38b_original.png/43e4513b9104ea0d68c9c096cea374ba8440dde3e027af5465c8771e8839a67c","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/726/e66916f9112a11c1e97ec5ea0ad886121d14f38b_original.png/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c","xtralarge":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/726/e66916f9112a11c1e97ec5ea0ad886121d14f38b_original.png/c11036e2d3f8b05af4b5da5984ccdec6f786b763c8abceb4e68042e10dcdae85"}}}]}